Home Check operates from 8am to 5pm, Monday - Friday. An after hours emergency maintenance line operates outside these times.

After hours maintenance is very expensive and we need to advise that if you use this service and the problem is not of the type described below, you may be charged the call out fee for this service. The approximate minimum call out charge is at least $200.00.
